veral Air Force Station: A [[Delta II]] carrying the [[GPS IIR-1]] satellite explodes 13 seconds after launch, dropping 250 tons of burning rocket remains around the launch pad. *[[1998]] &ndash; [[Lewinsky scandal]]: [[Matt Drudge]] breaks the story of the [[Bill Clinton]]–[[Monica Lewinsky]] affair on his ''[[Drudge Report]]'' website. *[[2002]] &ndash; [[Mount Nyiragongo]] erupts in the [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]], displacing an estimated 400,000 people. *[[2007]] &ndash; The [[Doomsday Clock]] is set to five minutes to midnight in response to [[North Korea]]'s nuclear testing. *[[2010]] &ndash; [[2010 Jos riots|Rioting]] begins between Muslim and Christian groups in [[Jos|Jos, Nigeria]], results in at least 200 deaths.
